# ── MusicMind AI Recommender · Environment Variables ──────────────────────────
#
# 1. Copy this file:   cp .env.example .env
# 2. Fill in your key: get it FREE at https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# 3. Run the app:      streamlit run app.py
